WWW::Shorten


   Abstract interface to URL shortening sites.


For installation details, see INSTALL.

For usage, see the doco. Either use perldoc or view it
on the web at:
    <http://search.cpan.org/author/SPOON/WWW-Shorten/>

Changes for 1.85 (30 Aug 2003)
   - Added v3.net
   - Assorted documentation tidyups.
   - Changed URL for shorlfilter.
   - Fixed qURL documentation.
   - Added tinylink.com
   - SmLnk.pm now uses the SmLnk API.


For a complete list of changes, see the Changes file.


by Iain Truskett.
